Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.88,0:57:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,members are below 200?\N>> That is a problem. You're adopted.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.64,0:57:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it is. You're adopted.\N>> No, it it is a problem. It is a problem
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.79,0:57:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,especially in 12step groups where one\Nperson is forced by the severity of the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.44,0:57:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,calamity to\Nuh join a spiritual group and they are
