Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.16,0:57:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,either you surrender to God and\Nand learn to be honest etc. or croak. A
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.55,0:57:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,lot of people choose God.\NThey then become quite spiritually
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.20,0:57:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,oriented. They start telling about easy\Ndoes it, live and less live, first
