Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.31,0:58:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,considerable disparity and it certainly\Nleads to divorce very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.68,0:58:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If only one member of the family starts\Ngetting committed to spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.04,0:58:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,evolution, there may be considerable\Ndisparity with other members of the
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.79,0:58:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,family and it is a frequent cause of\Ndivorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.64,0:58:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If salvation and enlightenment both lead\Nto the same end and enlightenment is a
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.24,0:58:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,more demanding road to follow, what is\Nthe reason one would focus on the path
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.59,0:58:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of enlightenment?\NOh, we explained earlier salvation and
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.24,0:58:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightenment are two different things.\NSalvation means to reach the level of
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.76,0:58:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,love, especially unconditional love.\NEnlightenment you're looking at 800 to
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.24,0:58:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,a,000.\NEnlightenment is just as more advanced,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.48,0:58:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,more difficult, more arduous and\Nextremely difficult to
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.92,0:59:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,extremely difficult on this planet. Now\Nit's extremely difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.16,0:59:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's extreme consumably difficult to get\Nto 540 to get beyond 600 we said happens
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.48,0:59:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,one in 10 million.\NTo get to 700 is less than even that. To
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.68,0:59:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,go beyond that is practically never\Nhappens.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.44,0:59:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Centuries and centuries go by without a\Nsingle individual going that high. And
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.31,0:59:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,when they do reach such levels, it is\Nextremely arduous. And without special
