Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.55,0:59:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,540 to 600. It's not made for it. And uh\Nunder special conditions with an
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.96,1:00:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,intensity\Nof rockhard steel like immutable
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.31,1:00:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,commitment\Nis not possible. So you know it must be
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.83,1:00:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,a rather unique peculiar\Nuh
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.92,1:00:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,thing to do. You know, how many times\Nhas anybody reached over 850, 900 in
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.83,1:00:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,man's history, you know, on the\Noccasional centuries go by.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.68,1:00:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with the evolution of\Nconsciousness and how it chooses to
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.52,1:00:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,express itself. It has to do with\Ncommitments that were karmically made
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.35,1:00:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and\Nthe willingness to be of service to God
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.76,1:00:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what.\NBeyond the ordinary beyond the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.88,1:00:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows why?\N>> Yes. We'll stop. One more question.
